OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FForced meter installations 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsuspended for six weeks    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The energy watchdog has told suppliers 
OL,6, to suspend forced prepayment meter     
OL,7, installations for the next six weeks.  
OL,9,FIn a letter sent to energy companies on
OL,10,FWednesday, Ofgem told them to halt     
OL,11,Fforced installations and remote        
OL,12,Ftransfers to prepayment meters until   
OL,13,Fthe end of March 2023.                 
OL,15,FOfgem said all domestic suppliers had  
OL,16,Fagreed to do so.                       
OL,18,FThe regulator will consult on how firms
OL,19,Fshould use prepayment meters and       
OL,20,Fwhether the rules should be changed.   
